item.content:encoded:
How We Do It

Work process

LOD 100

Conceptual

Providing proposals to the client for preliminary approval with the full models rendering.

LOD 200

Schematic

Performing 3D building models for perspective as agreed concept and function space program.

LOD 350

Development

Providing proposals to the client for preliminary approval with disciplinary spaces.

LOD 450

Tendering

Finalize the bill of quantity and technical documents for the contractor tendering.

LOD 500

Construction

Executing the site work with conditions, time frame and approved budgets.
